The story of 1999 unfolds further. It seems more than just The Hex were infected with strange new powers… Meanwhile, the Technocyte Coda rises and new stories and characters emerge in the latest addition to Warframe.

Caught in a web of time travel, Infestation, and heavy metal madness, you’ll encounter Temple, the guitar-wielding glam rocker, alongside four new Protoframes with matching Gemini Skins. Navigate the tangled pasts of Flare, Kaya, Minerva, and Velimir  — whether mending the broken bond between Minerva and Velimir or facing Flare’s battle against Scaldra. New Adversaries, weapons, skins, and missions await in Techrot Encore!

Prepare for an unforgettable ride through time and battle. The echoes of 1999 are calling; it’s up to you to answer.

author: PlayStation
description:
You are a demon in the Underworld, made out of glass and pain. The Devil has given you a skateboard with a simple deal: Skate to the Moon and swallow it — and you shall be freed.

Ollie, kickflip, and grind your way through the ash and smoke of The Emptylands as you take on a seemingly impossible quest. Learn to master your weight and motion to conquer the weeping concrete. Savour the ritualistic beauty as you set your feet to pop a perfect kickflip.

Skate fast to destroy vicious demons, help a forgetful frog, and save other tortured souls on your journey from fragile beginner to a hardened skater. Push through hell and discover The Devil’s greatest weakness: humility, perseverance, and a disgustingly sweet backside tailslide.

All you need is your skateboard.

author: PlayStation
description:
Ruffy and the Riverside is a platformer adventure that lets you change the world. Just grab a texture and throw it somewhere else and the world will change! Transform water into ice to cross an ocean. Throw a climbing vine onto a waterfall to climb a mountain. With the magic Swap you can exchange materials, symbols, colors, even the sun for the moon. Explore the open world, collect treasures, solve puzzles, fight, skate and unleash your imagination. Once you SWAP, you can't stop!
Ruffy and the Riverside is coming to PlayStation 5 on June 26.
